CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 31, 1946, pg. 5 reads: "Visits Cousins - Accompanied by her brother, Roderick, Miss Eltie Charles of Baltimore, Md., is visiting her cousins, Mr. and Mrs. William S. Jones of Sylvania Avenue. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Eltie Charles wearing dark short sleeved top with wrap around front, clip-on earrings, and brooch, posed in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
